{
  "translationLines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 237792,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "神々は地上への干渉を徹底的に禁じられ、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The gods were thoroughly forbidden from interfering with the surface world,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237793,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "地上に居ることはもちろん、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Of course, they were prohibited from being on the surface,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237794,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "地上を覗くことすら禁じられたのだった。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and even spying on the surface was forbidden."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237795,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "これはクエルプランにとって、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "For Quelpplan,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237796,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ある日突然、恋を奪われたも同然だった。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "it was as if love had been suddenly taken away one day."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237797,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "一部の神は、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Some of the gods,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237798,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ルールの網の目をかいくぐるように、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "slipping through the mesh of the rules,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237799,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "地上に残る者、地上の監視を続ける者もいた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "there were those who remained on the surface and those who continued to watch over it."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237800,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "しかし、クエルプランに",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "However, Quelpplan"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237801,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "それらの悪知恵を働かせることは出来ない。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "was not able to use such cunning."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237802,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "結果、唯一の娯楽であった、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "As a result, the only entertainment"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237803,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ランスの観察も封じられ、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "of watching Rance was also forbidden,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237804,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "何年も、ただ想いを募らせ続けた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and for years, she only continued to yearn."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237805,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "…………",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "…………"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237806,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "……"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237807,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "天界、上層部――",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Heaven, upper levels――"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237808,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ここは天界において最も地上に近い場所。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "This is the place closest to the surface in all of heaven."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237809,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "今は完全に封鎖された、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Now completely sealed off,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237810,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "人間の暮らす世界への入り口。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "the entrance to the human world."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237811,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "人間さえ来られない土地。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "A land even humans cannot enter."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237812,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「…………」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"…………\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237813,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "クエルプランは暇さえあれば、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Whenever she had free time, Quelpplan"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237814,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ここに来るようになっていた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "had come to this place."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237815,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ランス……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Rance…\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237816,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ここから先には神は絶対に行けない。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "No god is absolutely allowed beyond here."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237817,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "そうルールを定められてしまったからである。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Because the rules have been strictly established as such."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237818,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「今……貴方はどこでどうしているの……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Right now... where are you and what are you doing...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237819,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「神は……人に、恋をする権利すらないの……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Gods... don’t even have the right to fall in love with humans...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237820,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ああ……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ah...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237821,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "もう何度目の胸の痛みだろう。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "She wondered how many times her heart had ached like this."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237822,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ギリギリと締め上げられるような痛みが走る。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "A pain like being tightened sharply ran through her."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237823,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ポロリと――",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Suddenly――"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237824,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "涙が溢れてこぼれた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "tears overflowed and spilled."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237825,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「とても、辛いです……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"It’s so painful...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237826,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「……とても、苦しい」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...So very hard to bear.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237827,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「こんなことなら……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"If it were like this...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237828,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　神になど生まれたくなかった……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I never wanted to be born a god...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237829,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「同じ人間なら……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"If I were a human too...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237830,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　自由に恋をすることだって……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I could freely fall in love...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237831,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「私は……人間になりたかった……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I... wanted to become human...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237832,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "クエルプランは、以前女神ALICEの",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Quelpplan recalled a proposal from the goddess ALICE long ago."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237833,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ある提案を断ったことを思い出していた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "She remembered having refused that proposal."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237834,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "それはランスを殺し、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "It involved killing Rance,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237835,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "魂を自分の物として永遠に保管するというもの。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and eternally keeping his soul as her own."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237836,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "それはクエルプランの思う理想とは",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Since it was completely contrary to Quelpplan's ideals,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237837,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "まったくかけ離れていた為、即座に断った。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "she immediately refused."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237838,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "しかし、こんなことになるくらいなら……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "But if it would come to this..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237839,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "せめて。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "At least."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237840,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "詮無きこととは言え、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Though it would be useless,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237841,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "そんなことまで思ってしまう。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "she even found herself thinking such thoughts."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237842,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "後悔することが、これほどに辛いことと、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Quelpplan knew for the first time, after thousands of years of life, how painful regret could be."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237843,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "クエルプランは何千年も生きて初めて知った。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Regretting something is such a painful thing,\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237844,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「おや……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Oh…"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237845,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　これはこれは……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Well, well…\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237846,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "クエルプランが無表情の顔を上げる。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Quelpplan lifted her expressionless face."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237847,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "この土地で自分以外の者に会うのが初めてなら、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "It was her first time meeting anyone else in this land,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237848,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "誰かの声を聞くのも初めてのことだった。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and also the first time hearing another’s voice."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237849,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「なんともおいたわしいですなぁ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"How utterly mischievous.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237850,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "その老人は、闇からわき出るように、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The old man appeared quietly,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 237851,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "そっと姿を現した。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "as if emerging from the darkness."
    }
  ]
}

